#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-ops/src/ch_ops_projects_users.xml:72
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add project members and adjust the project quotas. "
"We'll discuss those later, but in practice it can be quite convenient to "
"deal with all these operations at one time."
msgstr ""
"プロジェクトメンバーを追加し、プロジェクトのクォータを調整することもできま"
"す。後述しますが、これらの操作を一度にすべて処理するほうが、実践的には非"
"常に便利です。"

